snippet.title: Frozen Synapse: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.frozensynapse.com

[Will be released on 26.05.2011 - pre-order available now!]

Frozen Synapse is the ultimate tactical game for PC and Mac - out now!

Trailer music is by nervous_testpilot and is available as part of the Frozen Synapse Soundtrack Bundle.
